  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2019-10-11",
    "date": "2021-09-01T20:21:22Z",
    "text": "Affordable Pricing for Taxpayer-Funded Prescription Drugs Act of 2019\n\nThis bill prohibits federal agencies and nonprofit entities that conduct federally funded health care research from providing a patent for a drug based on such research until the entity receiving the patent enters into a reasonable pricing agreement with the Department of Health and Human Services."
